description: Jessi Peine and her husband Charlie Johnson are taking Peeps Hot Box through Minneapolis and pleasing all the people with their positively flavor-packed offerings.Jessi, with her extensive culinary experience, has taken the best flavors from places like Japan, Mexico, Vietnam, and France, in order to craft an eclectic selection of worldly cuisine. Using only high quality locally sourced ingredients, their seasonal menu is all made-from-scratch, and includes dishes like Yakitori Chicken with a savory soy glaze, Banh Mi that’s brimming with juicy pork, heavenly Huaraches, and so much more. Pop on by Peeps Hot Box to try any of this deliciousness, and you too will agree that the food from this truck absolutely rocks.
name: Peeps Hot Box
